@page "/"
@inherits BaseComponent

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo="Typo.h3" GutterBottom="true">SimRegis Portal</MudText>

<MudText Class="mb-8">
    Welcome to your all-in-one solution for managing work hours, time-off, and payroll with precision and ease.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-2">
    SimRegisPortal is a modern platform designed for IT companies that need full control over internal work time tracking and salary processing.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-2">
    Employees can log their working hours manually, allowing for flexible and accurate time tracking across tasks and projects.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-2">
    Managers have the ability to review, approve, or reject submitted time records in just a few clicks, keeping workflows clean and transparent.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-2">
    SimRegisPortal also supports tracking of vacation and sick leaves, integrating these into the overall time balance automatically.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mb-2">
    The system calculates salaries based on submitted hours and leave data, while also automatically applying tax and social deductions, ensuring every payout is accurate and compliant.
</MudText>